text: Nijat is an Azerbaijani male given name that may refer to *Nijat Abasov (born 1995), Azerbaijani chess player *Nijat Mammadov (born 1985), Azerbaijani chess player *Nijat Rahimov (born 1993), Azerbaijani-Kazakhstani weightlifter *Nijat Shikhalizade (born 1988), Azerbaijani judoka Category:Azerbaijani masculine given names
title: Nijat (given name)
